kground\n- :foreground - default text color\n\nAlso:\n- noticed membrane.term was crashing when I tried\n  https://github.com/sharkdp/bat. Added support for 24-bit colors.\n- made some very minor clj-kondo recommended cleanups\n\nNotes:\n- Minimal, but adequate, error handling included for iterm color\n  scheme loading.\n- Terminal resize functionality unchanged but you'll notice that\n  background color does not grow to larger size.\n- I made some guesses on how to use skia, some of them were\n  likely naive.\n\nCloses #1","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/phronmophobic/membrane.term/commits/0faaa8d246b25663c02a22101617a82bdc3f680e","html_url":"https://github.com/phronmophobic/membrane.term/commit/0faaa8d246b25663c02a22101617a82bdc3f680e","diff":null,"files":null,"repository_full_name":"phronmophobic/membrane.term","comments":null,"author":null,"committer":null,"created_at":"2021-10-28T10:17:02.000-04:00","display_url":"https://github.com/phronmophobic/membrane.term/commit/0faaa8d246b25663c02a22101617a82bdc3f680e","display_title":"Support color schemes"},{"sha":"0faaa8da91a8b93b2004a2d2c1fac0f15d26931c","message":"cambio en diaMayorValorxAccion.pig","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/cpatin10/telematica-bigdata/commits/0faaa8da91a8b93b2004a2d2c1fac0f15d26931c","html_url":"https://github.com/cpatin10/telematica-bigdata/commit/0faaa8da91a8b93b2004a2d2c1fac0f15d26931c","diff":null,"files":null,"repository_full_name":"cpatin10/telematica-bigdata","comments":null,"author":null,"committer":null,"created_at":"2018-05-05T11:24:10.000-05:00","display_url":"https://github.com/cpatin10/telematica-bigdata/commit/0faaa8da91a8b93b2004a2d2c1fac0f15d26931c","display_title":"cambio en diaMayorValorxAccion.pig"},{"sha":"0faaa8d04c8c1994883eb9c737ba4383d2ba6513","message":"Create Circular linked list","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/aankitkumaar/Newton-School-Assignment/commits/0faaa8d04c8c1994883eb9c737ba4383d2ba6513","html_url":"https://github.com/aankitkumaar/Newton-School-